---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "About Tau Labs — custom AI hardware and conversational AI integration for SMBs.",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20 sm:px-8">
		<h1 class="mb-12 text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary">About Tau Labs</h1>
		
		<div class="mb-20">
			<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">Our Mission</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
				To bridge the gap between AI concept and shipped product. We provide the engineering rigor and manufacturing execution needed to bring intelligent devices to market at scale.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-20">
			<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">Our Story</h2>
			<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
				<p>
					Founded by engineers from the University of Pennsylvania and based in Philadelphia, PA, we started Tau Labs because we saw a gap in the market. While large tech companies were shipping incredible voice-enabled devices, smaller product teams struggled to execute. The challenge wasn't just the AI—it was the supply chain, the firmware stability, and the factory integration.
				</p>
				<p>
					We believe that conversational AI belongs in toys, tools, appliances, and robots. But it requires more than just code. It requires a partner who understands the entire lifecycle—from the first prototype to the final assembly line. We bring that certainty to teams of all sizes.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-20">
			<h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">Manufacturing & Scale</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
				<div>
					<p class="text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
						<span class="text-text-primary font-bold">We are not a software agency. We ship hardware.</span>
						Our team has deep roots in the Shenzhen supply chain and US-based product engineering. We don't just prototype; we design for yield, testability, and longevity.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-accent font-bold mt-1">1M+</span>
							<span>Units shipped across prior ventures in consumer electronics and IoT.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="text-accent font-bold mt-1">Tier-1</span>
							<span>Manufacturing partners in Guangdong and Vietnam for scalable production.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-gray-900/50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-800">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-lg font-bold text-text-primary">Advisory Board & Partners</h3>
					<ul class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary text-sm">
						<li class="border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">
							<div class="font-bold text-text-primary">Ex-Supply Chain Lead, DJI</div>
							<div>Advising on DFM and quality control processes.</div>
						</li>
						<li class="border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">
							<div class="font-bold text-text-primary">Senior Audio Engineer, Sonos</div>
							<div>Advising on acoustic design and far-field voice capture.</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<div class="font-bold text-text-primary">Strategic Sourcing Partner</div>
							<div>Direct access to Tier-1 flash and SoC distributors.</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mb-20">
			<h2 class="mb-8 text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">Our Values</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">Execution First</h3>
					<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">We focus on shipping. Prototypes are easy; mass production is hard. We excel at the hard part.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">Privacy by Design</h3>
					<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">We prioritize on-device processing to keep user data safe and secure, ensuring COPPA/GDPR compliance.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-6">
					<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-bold text-text-primary">Technical Certainty</h3>
					<p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">We define BOM, power, and latency targets upfront, reducing risk and eliminating surprises.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
